Text: This was the first video done by BeautyLeg and you can see the photographer has made a lot of improvement since then.  He was moving the camera a lot and that makes things jumpy.  But we love that photographer and hope he keeps making new vids for us.
I need your help seeding, gentlemen!  I want to post more sets, but can't leave one unseeded.  There's a lot more to come, so please play the game so I can give you more.
